# Flowchart Template

graph TD
    A[Start: Process Name] --> B{Decision Point?}

    B -->|Yes| C[Action 1]
    B -->|No| D[Action 2]

    C --> E[Process Step]
    D --> E

    E --> F{Another Decision?}
    F -->|Continue| G[Next Step]
    F -->|End| H[End Process]

    G --> I[Final Step]
    I --> J([Success])

    H --> K([Complete])

    %% Styling (optional)
    classDef processClass fill:#e1f5fe,stroke:#01579b,stroke-width:2px
    classDef decisionClass fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#ef6c00,stroke-width:2px
    classDef terminalClass fill:#e8f5e8,stroke:#2e7d32,stroke-width:2px

    class A,C,D,E,G,I processClass
    class B,F decisionClass
    class J,K terminalClass
